
## 🔄 WebGPU Migration - Gap Analysis & Action Items

### Overview
Migration from WebGL GLSL shaders to WebGPU TSL (Three.js Shading Language).

**Current State:**
- WebGL: ~22 shader files, 9 rendering stages, full Disney BSDF, ~110+ configurable parameters
- WebGPU: ~18 TSL files, 4 stages, basic path tracing with partial BSDF

---

